    <main>
        <p>This mobile app project focused on developing a task management app that helps users track and manage their daily tasks and deadlines. It was built for both iOS and Android platforms using React Native.</p>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400" alt="Mobile App Mockup">

        <h3>Steps Taken to Complete the Project:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Designed the UI/UX for the app using Adobe XD</li>
            <li>Developed the mobile app using React Native</li>
            <li>Implemented local notifications to remind users of tasks</li>
            <li>Integrated a cloud database (Firebase) to store user data</li>
            <li>Tested the app and launched it on both iOS and Android</li>
        </ol>
